After hitting [Seed] it'll tell me "0/100% 0 Seeds", but clicking on it eventually loads the full image. Does pinning actually work? Because it seems to miss a bunch of images since [Seed] with "0 Seeds" still remains, but do eventually load if I expand the image.

Am I actually seeding the whole board? Goddamn why is this shit so annoying?

Also I'm not getting a bunch of notifications when I enter a thread of a board I pinned.
